 
<p>
A US appeals court agreed that Monsanto and other companies are responsible
for the <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/news/2022/07/07/just-beginning-appeals-court-affirms-pesticide-giants-liable-dicamba-drift">damage done when dicamba, a herbicide, drifted onto an orchard
from nearby farms</a>.
<p>
Dicamba is used on genetically modified soybeans and cotton.

 